comments: After initially making contact with the ball, Johnson (SAS) pulls Hart's (NYK) left arm and causes him to lose his balance.
Wembanyama (SAS) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with McBride (NYK).
Hartenstein (NYK) places his forearm against Wembanyama's (SAS) body as both players elevate for the ball and the contact is marginal.
Jones's (SAS) arm is not in a vertical position when he moves forwards into Brunson (NYK) and initiates illegal contact to his right shoulder.
McBride (NYK) and Vassell (SAS) briefly engage and disengage with one another prior to Vassell gathering the pass.
Jones (SAS) establishes himself with his forearm slightly extended and marginal contact occurs with McBride's (NYK) side as he defends over the pick.
Jones (SAS) swipes down at the ball as DiVincenzo (NYK) controls the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Brunson (NYK) places his forearm against Jones (SAS) and releases away without applying force as he gathers into his shooting motion.
Hartenstein (NYK) briefly grasps Wembanyama's (SAS) arm during the rebound.
Hartenstein (NYK) Initiates contact to Wembanyama's (SAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brunson (NYK) places his forearm against Jones (SAS) and releases away without applying force as he gathers into his shooting motion.
Johnson (SAS) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Jones (SAS) moves parallel alongside of Brunson (NYK) with a forearm resting against his body and the contact during his driving shot attempt is marginal.
DiVincenzo (NYK) leans into Wembanyama (SAS), whose FOM is unaffected.
Vassell (SAS) makes incidental foot to foot contact with McBride (NYK) as he trails behind him.
McBride (NYK) establishes himself in Jones' (SAS) path as he sets the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Vassell (SAS) briefly places a hand on Brunson's (NYK) body during the driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Johnson (SAS) jumps alongside Robinson (NYK) and brushes his arm during the shot attempt near the rim.
Wembanyama (SAS) briefly has his hand on the ball before Robinson (NYK) gains full control.
Robinson (NYK) reaches in and deflects the ball away from Wembanyama (SAS) and out of bounds.
Robinson (NYK) moves laterally into Wembanyama (SAS) during his drive to the basket and initiates leg contact that causes him to trip.
Robinson (NYK) taps the jump ball before the ball reaches its apex.
Brunson (NYK) and Jones (SAS) mutually engage and then disengage off ball.
McBride (NYK) briefly rests a hand on Vassell (SAS) before deflecting the pass.
Wembanyama (SAS) establishes himself in McBride's (NYK) path and marginal occurs to McBride's side as Wembanyama slips away to roll to the basket.
Robinson (NYK) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and SAS should have retained possession.
Jones (SAS) moves laterally into Brunson's (NYK) path and initiates body contact that affects Brunson's SQBR during his drive to the basket.
Brunson (NYK) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes more than two steps as he gathers into his jump shot.
Achiuwa (NYK) briefly has an arm around Wembanyama's (SAS) lower body and incidental foot contact between the two players causes Wembanyama to lose his balance.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: DiVincenzo (NYK) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Hart (NYK) commits a take foul on Jones (SAS).
Achiuwa (NYK) briefly has a hand placed against Wembanyama's (SAS) hip as the two players engage to establish position.
Brunson (NYK) grabs Jones (SAS) and affects his ability to receive the pass.
